_sText:
I was in art history class and i got inspired when we were going over Greek architecture

Right when i saw the model of the ancient Greek temple/Polis, i thought, "I'm gonna make that!"

so i did and here it is, its beta so there may be a couple small issues but i just wanted to get it out there because it is a fun map that i put a lot of thought/time into.
 
ENJOY!


BOMBSITES---
A= largest temple (inside)
B=center temple with horse statue
